Dear Sir or Madam,

I write in relation to the Defendants=E2=80=99 Summary Grounds of Resistance serv=
ed on 12 January 2026.

I confirm that the Claimant intends to file a Reply. That Reply will rely o=
n a structured evidential dataset derived from contemporaneous correspondenc=
e covering the period from February 2024 onwards, addressing the Claimant=E2=80=99=
s ability to participate in proceedings and ongoing administrative matters.

The dataset is currently being finalised and systematised. I respectfully n=
otify the Court that the Claimant=E2=80=99s Reply will be filed shortly once that =
process is complete.

I would be grateful if this notification could be placed on the court file.

Yours faithfully,

Nadia Zahmoul
Claimant (Litigant in Person)

